OL,3,CDisgraced top lawyer has appeal
OL,4,Cagainst prison sentence rejected
OL,6,FA disgraced Jersey defence lawyer will
OL,7,Fstay behind bars after having his
OL,8,Fappeal against a seven-month prison
OL,9,Fsentence rejected.
OL,11,FDavid Steenson, 57, previously
OL,12,Fadmitted failing to stop after an
OL,13,Faccident, drink-driving and two counts
OL,14,Fof dangerous driving.
OL,16,FIn May, the court heard how Steenson
OL,17,Fstruck a Mini Cooper with his vehicle
OL,18,Fand left the scene, driving whilst
OL,19,Fmore than double the legal alcohol
OL,20,Flimit and leaving the other motorist
OL,21,Fwith whiplash and sleeping issues.
