OL,6,FIt was the second time he had appeared
OL,7,Fin the dock in the last 12 months,
OL,8,Fpreviously receiving community service
OL,9,Ffor attacking a taxi driver whilst
OL,10,Fdrunk.
OL,12,FRepresenting himself at the appeal
OL,13,Fhearing for these latest offences,
OL,14,FSteenson told Jersey's Bailiff and
OL,15,Fsitting Jurats that this was "make or
OL,16,Fbreak" for him and he was genuinely
OL,17,Fremorseful.
