OL,6,FSteenson also said he did not want his
OL,7,Ffamily paying the price but the
OL,8,FBailiff responded that "if a defendant
OL,9,Fcan't take his family into account at
OL,10,Fthe time, it's a bit rich to expect
OL,11,Fthe court to".
OL,13,FThe prosecution stated that the
OL,14,FMagistrate did not pass a wrong
OL,15,Fjudgment and said it cannot seriously
OL,16,Fbe argued that the term exceeded the
OL,17,Fsentencing guidelines.
